{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "0df81e05-2d4e-4f24-9b2f-db3bfb81096a",
		"name": "Moleculer JS Microservice Auth API",
		"description": "Koleksi endpoint untuk menguji Boilerplate Autentikasi berbasis Moleculer JS.\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Jalankan server: `npm run dev`\n2. Eksekusi **2. User Login** terlebih dahulu — token JWT akan otomatis tersimpan ke env variable `jwt_token`\n3. Semua request protected sudah terkonfigurasi menggunakan `{{jwt_token}}`",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Grup endpoint terkait autentikasi (Registrasi, Login, dan Profil).",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "1. User Registration",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"email\": \"johndoe@email.com\"\n}",
							"options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Mendaftarkan pengguna baru ke sistem."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "2. User Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"if (jsonData && jsonData.token) {",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.token);",
									"    console.log(\"Token automatically saved to environment variables!\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
							"options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Login dan dapatkan JWT token.\n\n*Catatan: Script Postman pada endpoint ini telah dikonfigurasi untuk menangkap nilai token balasan secara otomatis dan memindahkannya ke Environment Variable `jwt_token`. Anda tinggal mengeksekusi request berikutnya tanpa perlu copy-paste token manual!*"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "3. Get My Profile (Protected)",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{ "key": "token", "value": "{{jwt_token}}", "type": "string" }
							]
						},
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
						},
						"description": "Endpoint yang terotorisasi. Hanya pengguna yang menyematkan `Bearer Token` di bagian HTTP header (Authorization) yang dapat mengakses ini. Token tersebut diambil otomatis dari hasil login."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		}
	],
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [""] }
		},
		{
			"listen": "test",
			"script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [""] }
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:3000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "jwt_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	]
}